		"description": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At the sight of incoming danger, you briefly call up a warding shield around yourself and nearby allies.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you or an ally within 15 feet are targeted by a spell with a duration of 1 round or less, you may briefly manifest a 5-foot-square shield centered in front of the target. The creature gains threequarters cover against the spell, potentially turning a hit into a miss. You may also spend up to a total of 3 exertion on this reaction, protecting one extra creature within range for each additional point spent.</span></p>",
